padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Turin, Ronaldo n\u00f3i anh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng theo c\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 1 trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t cho chuy\u1ebfn x\u00ea d\u1ecbch \u0111\u00e3 \u0111ang v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00f3i t\u1edbi r\u1ea9t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ee7a CR7. T\u1eeb Real t\u1edbi Juve. T\u1eeb Madrid t\u1edbi Turin. T\u1eeb Bernabeu t\u1edbi Juventus Arena.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Sau 9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, v\u1edbi 15 danh hi\u1ec7u trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 4 Champions League, 438 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, 450 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n cao qu\u00fd nh\u01b0 4 Ballon D&rsquo;or v\u00e0 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t k\u1ec9 l\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n v\u00f4 ti\u1ec1n kho\u00e1ng h\u1eadu, Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 chia tay Real Madrid. Juventus, CLB m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 1 trong nh\u1eefng &ldquo;n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n&rdquo; quen thu\u1ed9c c\u1ee7a anh v\u00e0 Real Madrid tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u1ea5p CLB v\u00e0i n\u0103m qua. </strong><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo cap ben Turin:  Juve co con la&hellip; Juve?\" title=\"Ronaldo c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Turin:  Juve c\u00f3 c\u00f2n l\u00e0&hellip; Juve?\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/ro.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ronaldo c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Turin:  Juve c\u00f3 c\u00f2n l\u00e0&hellip; Juve?</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nNg\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Turin, Ronaldo n\u00f3i anh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng theo c\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 1 trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t cho chuy\u1ebfn x\u00ea d\u1ecbch \u0111\u00e3 \u0111ang v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00f3i t\u1edbi r\u1ea9t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ee7a CR7. T\u1eeb Real t\u1edbi Juve. T\u1eeb Madrid t\u1edbi Turin. T\u1eeb Bernabeu t\u1edbi Juventus Arena.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong Ban gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a Real n\u00f3i, Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus v\u00ec \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, t\u1ea1i Italia, CR7 s\u1ebd ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 1 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n tranh c\u00e3i. Ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch thu\u1ebf \u1edf Italia, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tri\u1ec7u ph\u00fa n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i nh\u01b0 Ronaldo &ldquo;m\u1ec1m&rdquo; h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n so v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, n\u01a1i m\u00e0 Ronaldo v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed9p g\u1ea7n 20 tri\u1ec7u euro cho C\u01a1 quan Thu\u1ebf v\u1ee5 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edf t\u1ea1i v\u00ec&hellip; t\u1ed9i tr\u1ed1n thu\u1ebf thu nh\u1eadp b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u00e0i n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u1ea1i Juve, m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo trong b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 4 n\u0103m c\u0169ng cao h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a cu\u1ed1i \u1edf Real g\u1ea7n 5 tri\u1ec7u euro. Ng\u00e0y Juve v\u00e0 Real x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ronaldo, gi\u00e1 c\u1ed5 phi\u1ebfu Juve v\u1ecdt \u0111\u1ec9nh -&nbsp; l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau g\u1ea7n 50 th\u00e1ng. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd v\u1eabn t\u0103ng! 3 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ec5 ra m\u1eaft ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Ronlaod t\u1ea1i Turin h\u00f4m 17/7, m\u1ebb b\u00e1n Online \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ed1 7 c\u1ee7a Juve, v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3ng h\u01a1n n\u1eeda tri\u1ec7u chi\u1ebfc, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c tifosi mua s\u1ea1ch.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cho \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, khi m\u00e0 Ronaldo ch\u01b0a ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t ph\u00fat n\u00e0o cho Juve v\u00e0 anh ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong Tour du \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a &ldquo;B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0&rdquo; th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Juve- CR7 g\u1ee3i m\u1ed9t c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa &ldquo;\u00e1p phe&rdquo; si\u00eau \u0111\u1eb3ng v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i-kinh t\u1ebf. B\u00f3ng ch\u01b0a l\u1eafn v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea3 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Juve \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 C\u00fap! Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Juve, \u00f4ng Andre Agnelli nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua, trong c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f9ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n c\u1ee5m t\u1eeb &ldquo;Hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng Cristiano&rdquo;. V\u00e0 cho \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp. L\u01b0\u1ee3ng theo d\u00f5i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Juve tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Twitter v\u00e0 Instagram t\u0103ng v\u1ecdt trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Su quan tam cua nguoi ham mo toan dau se tang len nho viec Juventus chieu mo Cristiano Ronaldo.\" title=\"S\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ebd t\u0103ng l\u00ean nh\u1edd vi\u1ec7c Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Cristiano Ronaldo.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/juve-ro-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>S\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ebd t\u0103ng l\u00ean nh\u1edd vi\u1ec7c Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Cristiano Ronaldo.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng Cristiano&rdquo; khi\u1ebfn BL\u0110 Juve c\u00f2n t\u00ednh t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n d\u1ef1ng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng anh \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u khu v\u1ef1c s\u1ea7m u\u1ea5t v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4ng kh\u00e1ch du l\u1ecbch nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Turin d\u00f9 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn khi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng \u00edt c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Juve ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1nh l\u00f2ng. &ldquo;Hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng Cristiano&rdquo; th\u1eadm ch\u00ed d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u00f2n \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0a Zinedine Zindane tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juve, \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m vai tr\u00f2 gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Th\u1ec3 thao. &ldquo;Hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng Cristiano&rdquo; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1ed5i l\u00e0 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1edbi t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t ng\u00f4i sao \u1edf c\u00e1c CLB kh\u00e1c, nh\u01b0 Paul Pogba &ndash; c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 Juve \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp k\u1ec9 l\u1ee5c b\u00e1n trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed CLB khi \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 Man Utd 2 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00fac n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0103n theo. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn &ldquo;hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng Cristiano&rdquo; ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e0 th\u1eadt. Nh\u1edd Ronaldo, Juve \u0111ang l\u00e0 t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. V\u00e0 nh\u1edd th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Juve &ndash; Ronaldo, Serie A \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft sau h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t th\u1eadp k\u1ec9 v\u1eadt v\u00e3 trong b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1i. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi vi\u1ebft, 1 tifosi t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng n\u0103m cu\u1ed1i th\u1eadp ni\u00ean 90 c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf k\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Juventini nh\u01b0ng qu\u1ea3 th\u1eadt c\u0169ng \u0111ang s\u1ed1ng trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, trong c\u01a1n ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch v\u00ec Ronaldo, v\u00ec s\u1ef1 ch\u1ecbu ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1edd t\u1eeb Juventus, t\u1eadn s\u00e2u trong c\u00e1c C\u0110V b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia &ndash; kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eefng tifosi c\u1ee7a Juve, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi: Tr\u00ean ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 thu\u1ea7n t\u00fay, Ronaldo s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec cho Juve, cho Serie A v\u00e0 cho ch\u00ednh anh trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo toi Juventus\" title=\"Ronaldo toi Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/chu-tich-la-liga-tiet-lo-ly-do-ronaldo-chia-tay-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ronaldo s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec cho Juve, cho Serie A v\u00e0 cho ch\u00ednh anh trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc?</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Italia, Christian Panucci n\u00f3i sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 r\u1eddi Real. C\u00f2n Ronaldo, trong ng\u00e0y d\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Turin th\u00ec kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &ldquo;T\u00f4i ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi r\u1eddi Real. C\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebf th\u00fac. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho m\u1ed9t h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c m\u1edbi. V\u1edbi Juve&rdquo;. Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Ronaldo th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i Real, \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 33, v\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Champions League, v\u1edbi ki\u1ec7t t\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Gianluigi Buffon, v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 44 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau&hellip; 44 tr\u1eadn, l\u00e0 1 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng, CR7, trong m\u00f9a \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho Juve \u1edf Serie A, h\u1eb3n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m ai ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng Juve \u0111\u00e2u c\u1ea7n Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb Serie A v\u1edbi 7 Scudetto li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2011/12? M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Juve th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o l\u00e0 s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. Khi m\u00e0 Napoli c\u00f9ng l\u00fac chia tay nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 HLV Maurizio Sarri, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m Jorginho v\u00e0 nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng Marek Hamsik. Khi m\u00e0 Roma chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t n\u1ed1t ng\u00f4i sao trong khung g\u1ed7 Allison. Khi m\u00e0 Inter l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 5 n\u0103m l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i chia s\u1ee9c \u1edf Champions League. V\u00e0 khi m\u00e0 Milan ng\u1eadp ch\u00ecm trong kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed5i thay \u1edf c\u1ea5p th\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea7ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo nha chinh phuc cac danh hieu\" title=\"Ronaldo nha chinh phuc cac danh hieu\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/Juventus-chieu-mo-Cristiano-Ronaldo-Co-gia-tri-con-lon-hon-tien-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ronaldo nha chinh phuc cac danh hieu</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juve c\u1ea7n Ronaldo &ndash; 1 si\u00eau k\u1ec9 l\u1ee5c gia Champions League &ndash; cho cu\u1ed9c Th\u00e1nh chi\u1ebfn \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong h\u01a1n 2 th\u1eadp k\u1ec9 qua. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ef1c ti\u00eau v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i \u1ea5y, Juve ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t v\u00e0&hellip; th\u1eadt nhanh c\u00e1i g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 &ldquo;hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng Cristiano&rdquo; &ndash; l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. B\u1edfi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 Ronaldo d\u1eabu c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Juve ch\u1eafc th\u1eafng v\u00e0 th\u1eafng l\u1edbn trong c\u00e1c h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i &ndash; kinh t\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, \u0111\u1ea5y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 1 canh b\u1ea1c.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo l\u00e0 t\u1ea5m g\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, l\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn cho b\u1ea5t k\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o kh\u00e1t khao chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec9nh cao, l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng d\u1ebbo dai hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 d\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea1i. Nh\u01b0ng Ronaldo \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0 ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 &ldquo;Si\u00eau nh\u00e2n&rdquo;. T\u1ef1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n anh c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecdc c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed5i thay c\u1ee7a c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tu\u1ed5i b\u0103m, gi\u1edd CR7 c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi Ronaldo, m\u1ed9t Juve \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng b\u1eb1ng n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, m\u1ed9t Juve - bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho nh\u1eefng g\u00ec tinh t\u00fay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Calcio, m\u1ed9t Juve ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u - chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a 1 ng\u00f4i sao ki\u1ec7t xu\u1ea5t, li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i b\u1ea3n ng\u00e3 c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh? V\u00ec Ronaldo!<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t Juve khi-c\u00f3-Ronaldo s\u1ebd nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf?<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>ELFLACO (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1423","checkdouble":"191603"},{"date":"15:33 19/07","title":"15 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/15-hinh-anh-dang-chu-y-nhat-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh 4 n\u0103m c\u00f3 1 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb7c s\u1eafc t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u01b0\u1edbc Nga \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, m\u00e0 Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch FIFA th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn &ldquo;\u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ec9m c\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m&rdquo;. Sau 64 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Didier Deschamps sau khi Ph\u00e1p h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Croatia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-2.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng k\u00e9o d\u00e0i su\u1ed1t 1 th\u00e1ng v\u1eeba qua, c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb7c s\u1eafc t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"h