\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/world-cup-2018-qua-nhung-con-so-tieu-bieu-421-191516.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/wc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/world-cup-2018-qua-nhung-con-so-tieu-bieu-421-191516.html\">World Cup 2018 qua nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u World Cup 2018, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/world-cup-2018-nhung-tran-cau-va-khoanh-khac-dang-nho-nhat-421-191457.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/world-cup-2018-nhung-tran-cau-va-khoanh-khac-dang-nho-nhat.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/world-cup-2018-nhung-tran-cau-va-khoanh-khac-dang-nho-nhat-421-191457.html\">World Cup 2018: Nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u v\u00e0 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb nh\u1ea5t</span><br>\r\nK\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ra nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Didier Deschamps, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/world-cup-2018-diem-qua-nhung-su-kien-noi-bat-nhat-421-191450.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/world-cup-2018-diem-qua-nhung-su-kien-noi-bat-nhat.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/world-cup-2018-diem-qua-nhung-su-kien-noi-bat-nhat-421-191450.html\">World Cup 2018: \u0110i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t</span><br>\r\nN\u01b0\u1edbc Nga \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1422","checkdouble":"191605"},{"date":"15:42 19/07","title":"S\u1ed1c: Nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Philippines d\u1ef1 AFF Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/soc-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-van-co-the-khoac-ao-philippines-du-aff-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Arsenal trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018: Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt th\u00f4ng tin l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u - LT\u0110 giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Arsenal nhanh v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u1ea5t.</h2>Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 chia tay HLV Arsene Wenger sau khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 h\u1ea1 m\u00e0n v\u00e0 c\u1ef1u HLV&nbsp;c\u1ee7a PSG, Unai Emery \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thay th\u1ebf. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p nh\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec3u Boreham Wood v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 8-0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu h\u00f4m 14/7 v\u1eeba qua.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00e8 2018 L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00e8 2018 L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/ars-153114285426350670822.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Arsenal</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1eafp t\u1edbi Arsenal s\u1ebd bay sang Singapore tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup 2018 (ICC Cup) v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 7. T\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t g\u1eb7p Atletico Madrid (26/7) v\u00e0 PSG (28/7).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 4/8 v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Sevilla, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery.<br>\r\n<h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Arsenal trong h\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n21h00 ng\u00e0y 14/7: Boreham Wood 0-8 Arsenal (Hertfordshire, Anh)<br>\r\n18h35 ng\u00e0y 26/7: Atletico Madrid vs Arsenal (Kallang, Singapore)<br>\r\n18h35 ng\u00e0y 28/7: Arsenal vs PSG (Kallang, Singapore)<br>\r\n02h05 ng\u00e0y 2/8: Arsenal vs Chelsea (Dublin, Ireland)<br>\r\n01h00 ng\u00e0y 4/8: Arsenal vs Sevilla (Stockholm, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lich-thi-dau-giao-huu-he-2018-cua-clb-chelsea-172-191609.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a CLB Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lich-thi-dau-giao-huu-he-2018-cua-mu-172-191607.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a MU</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1421","checkdouble":"191606"},{"date":"15:56 19/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/lich-thi-dau-giao-huu-he-2018-cua-mu.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a MU trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018: Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt th\u00f4ng tin l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u - LT\u0110 giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a MU nhanh v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u1ea5t.</h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-2019, CLB Man Utd s\u1ebd bay sang B\u1eafc M\u1ef9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0i tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf International Champions Cup (ICC 2018)\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/M_u-660.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a MU trong h\u00e8 2018 (gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam)</h2>\r\n09h00 ng\u00e0y 20/7: Man Utd - Club America<br>\r\n04h00 ng\u00e0y 23/07: Man Utd - SJ Earthquakes<br>\r\n10h05 ng\u00e0y 26/07: AC Milan - Man Utd (ICC 2018)<br>\r\n04h05 ng\u00e0y 29/07: Man Utd - Liverpool (ICC\u00a02018)<br>\r\n07h05 ng\u00e0y 01/08: Man Utd - Real Madrid (ICC\u00a02018)<br>\r\n01h15 ng\u00e0y 6/8: Bayern Munich - Man Utd<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1420","checkdouble":"191607"},{"date":"16:32 19/07","title":"Wilshere so s\u00e1nh HLV West Ham v\u1edbi Wenger","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/wilshere-so-sanh-pellegrini-voi-wenger.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Wilshere so s\u00e1nh Pellegrini v\u1edbi Wenger. Anh r\u1ea5t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i West Ham \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng khi kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Wilshere gia nh\u1eadp West Ham</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau m\u00f9a 2017/18, kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau khi HLV Arsene Wenger n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay Arsenal sau 22 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, Jack Wilshere c\u0169ng n\u1ed1i g\u00f3t. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 26 tu\u1ed5i h\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng gia h\u1ea1n. Anh gia nh\u1eadp West Ham theo giao k\u00e8o 3 n\u0103m d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCLB m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Wilshere hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. West Ham \u0111\u00e3 thay David Moyes b\u1eb1ng c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Man City, Manuel Pellegrini b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 Felipe Anderson hay Andriy Yarmolenko.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wilshere so s\u00e1nh Pellegrini v\u1edbi Wenger h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Wilshere so s\u00e1nh Pellegrini v\u1edbi Wenger h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/wilshere-so-sanh-pellegrini-voi-wenger.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Wilshere gia nh\u1eadp West Ham m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nC\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u00e2n thu\u1ed9c</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWilshere m\u1edbi b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 vui m\u1eebng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i cho West Ham. Anh c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u00e0 HLV Pellegrini s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh. Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0o gi\u1eefa Wenger v\u00e0 Pellegrini, Wilshere n\u00f3i: \u201cM\u1ed9t ch\u00fat, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1\u201d, Wilshere so s\u00e1nh Pellegrini v\u1edbi Wenger.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cPellegrini \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 CLB n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u t\u1eebng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u00f4i. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p, x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mong \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng \u00f4ng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Wenger\" title=\"HLV Wenger\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/4/wenger-thua-nhan-sai-lam-khi-o-lai-arsenal-qua-lau.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Wilshere so s\u00e1nh Pellegrini v\u1edbi Wenger</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nWilshere \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 CLB li\u00ean h\u1ec7 sau khi r\u1eddi Arsenal bao g\u1ed3m Fenerbahce \u1edf Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf l\u1ea1i Anh l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y ch\u1ecdn West Ham. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u00fd do l\u1edbn t\u00f4i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch vi\u00ean, HLV Anh\u201d, anh n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu c\u00f2n sung s\u1ee9c, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i cho \u0110T Anh. T\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. \u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 t\u00f4i t\u1eebng th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i CLB, nh\u01b0ng khi West Ham \u0111\u1eb7t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c. T\u00f4i l\u1edbn l\u00ean g\u1ea7n s\u00e2n Upton Park v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi CLB.\u201d<strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1419","checkdouble":"191608"}]}